## ResponseAssembler 输出格式
所有路径最终汇聚到统一格式：
```python
class AgentResponse(BaseModel):
    text: str
    charts: List[Dict[str, Any]] = []       # ECharts option list
    insight_report: Optional[InsightReport] = None
    response_type: Literal["query", "insight", "chat", "chart_update"]
```

